Feature: Managing Items


Background:
    GIVEN a released item exists
        AND a released engineering change exists


Scenario Outline: Create an Engineering Change Message for an Item
    WHEN <role> creates an index of the item with the engineering change
    THEN a new engineering change message is <state>
        AND it is <item_allocation> to the item
        AND it is <ec_allocation> to the engineering change

    Examples:
        | role         | state       | item_allocation | ec_allocation |
        | Engineering  | created     | allocated       | allocated     |


Scenario Outline: Delete an Engineering Change Message from an Item
    GIVEN an engineering change message for the item exists
    WHEN <role> deletes this engineering change message
    THEN the engineering change message is <state>
        AND the engineering change is <ec_state>
        AND the item is <item_state>

    Examples:
        | role        | state       | ec_state    | item_state  |
        | Engineering | not deleted | not deleted | not deleted |
